{"data":[{"name":"85:1","price":"星座を擁する天にかけて、¹","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡبُرُوجِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5910,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アーヤ*１－３の、アッラー*によるこの誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi dhāti al-burūji ","translations":["By the sky","containing","the constellations","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","dhāti","al-burūji",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3450],[2,3450,4120],[3,4120,8325]]}},{"name":"85:2","price":"また、約束された（復活の）日*にかけて、","arabic":"وَٱلۡيَوۡمِ ٱلۡمَوۡعُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5911,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-yawmi al-mawʿūdi ","translations":["And the Day","Promised","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-yawmi","al-mawʿūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,5245]]}},{"name":"85:3","price":"また、立ち会うものと立ち合われるものにかけて（誓う）、¹","arabic":"وَشَاهِدٖ وَمَشۡهُودٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5912,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「立ち会うもの（シャーヒド）」と「立ち会われるもの（マシュフード）」は、それぞれ「証言するもの、証言されるもの」とも解釈可能（イブン・ジュザイ２：５５５参照）。アル＝ワーヒディー*によれば、大半の解釈学者は前者と後者を、それぞれ「金曜日とアラファの日（ズル＝ヒッジャ*月九日）」と解釈しているが、その他「その逆」「預言者*ムハンマド*（雌牛章１４３、婦人章４１とその訳注を参照）と復活の日*（フード*章１０３参照）」「人間と復活の日*」など、非常に多くの説がある（２３：３８０－３８３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"washāhidin wamashhūdin ","translations":["And (the) witness","and what is witnessed","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["washāhidin","wamashhūdin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,6705]]}},{"name":"85:4","price":"堀の仲間たち¹が、成敗されますよう。","arabic":"قُتِلَ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡأُخۡدُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5913,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「堀の仲間たち」とは、信仰に入った自国民に対して、堀を掘ってその中に火をつけ、信仰を捨てなかった者をその中に放り込んで殺害した、不信仰者*の王とその手下たちのこと（ムスリム「信心深さと心温まる話の書」７３参照）。彼らが殺害した信仰者たちについては、「預言者*ムハンマド*が遣わされるより四十年前の、イエメンのキリスト教徒*」「イスラーイールの民*」「エチオピアの民」「ペルシャの民」などといった諸説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２８９－２９０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qutila aṣḥābu al-ukh'dūdi ","translations":["Destroyed were","(the) companions","(of) the pit","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["qutila","aṣḥābu","al-ukh'dūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1610],[3,1610,5935]]}},{"name":"85:5","price":"つまり、燃料がくべられた炎という（堀の）。","arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡوَقُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5914,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-nāri dhāti al-waqūdi ","translations":["(Of) the fire","full","(of) the fuel","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["al-nāri","dhāti","al-waqūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2120],[2,2120,2760],[3,2760,6735]]}},{"name":"85:6","price":"彼らが（信仰を棄てない信仰者たちを、その炎で罰するべく、）そこ（の淵）に腰かけた時のこと、","arabic":"إِذۡ هُمۡ عَلَيۡهَا قُعُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5915,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"idh hum ʿalayhā quʿūdun ","translations":["When","they","by it","(were) sitting","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["idh","hum","ʿalayhā","quʿūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,780],[3,780,1790],[4,1790,5425]]}},{"name":"85:7","price":"自分たちが信仰者たちにすること（懲罰）を、見物しつつ。","arabic":"وَهُمۡ عَلَىٰ مَا يَفۡعَلُونَ بِٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ شُهُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5916,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wahum ʿalā mā yafʿalūna bil-mu'minīna shuhūdun ","translations":["And they","over","what","they were doing","to the believers","witnesses","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wahum","ʿalā","mā","yafʿalūna","bil-mu'minīna","shuhūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1330],[3,1330,1730],[4,1730,3040],[5,3040,4550],[6,4550,8555]]}},{"name":"85:8","price":"そして、彼ら（堀の仲間たち）が彼ら（信仰者たち）を咎めたのは、彼ら（信仰者たち）が偉力ならびなく*、称賛されるべき*アッラー*を信じるがゆえに外ならなかった。","arabic":"وَمَا نَقَمُواْ مِنۡهُمۡ إِلَّآ أَن يُؤۡمِنُواْ بِٱللَّهِ ٱلۡعَزِيزِ ٱلۡحَمِيدِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5917,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā naqamū min'hum illā an yu'minū bil-lahi al-ʿazīzi al-ḥamīdi ","translations":["And not","they resented","[of] them","except","that","they believed","in Allah","the All-Mighty","the Praiseworthy","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","naqamū","min'hum","illā","an","yu'minū","bil-lahi","al-ʿazīzi","al-ḥamīdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1450],[3,1450,2250],[4,2250,4480],[5,4480,4959],[6,4959,6739],[7,6739,7839],[8,7839,8919],[9,8919,12274]]}},{"name":"85:9","price":"諸天と大地の王権が属するお方（であるアッラー*）を。アッラー*は、全てのことの証人であられる。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي لَهُۥ مُلۡكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِۚ وَٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيۡءٖ شَهِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5918,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī lahu mul'ku al-samāwāti wal-arḍi wal-lahu ʿalā kulli shayin shahīdun ","translations":["The One Who","for Him","(is) the dominion","(of) the heavens","and the earth","and Allah","on","every","thing","(is) a Witness","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","lahu","mul'ku","al-samāwāti","wal-arḍi","wal-lahu","ʿalā","kulli","shayin","shahīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,1590],[3,1590,2270],[4,2270,3760],[5,3760,5210],[6,5210,6260],[7,6260,6830],[8,6830,7480],[9,7480,9300],[10,9300,13455]]}},{"name":"85:10","price":"本当に、信仰者の男たちと信仰者の女たちを火（という試練）にかけ、その後に悔悟しなかった者たち、彼らにこそは地獄の懲罰があり、彼らにこそは、（焼き尽くす）炎の懲罰がある。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ فَتَنُواْ ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ وَٱلۡمُؤۡمِنَٰتِ ثُمَّ لَمۡ يَتُوبُواْ فَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ جَهَنَّمَ وَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ ٱلۡحَرِيقِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5919,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna fatanū al-mu'minīna wal-mu'mināti thumma lam yatūbū falahum ʿadhābu jahannama walahum ʿadhābu al-ḥarīqi ","translations":["Indeed","those who","persecuted","the believing men","and the believing women","then","not","they repented","then for them","(is the) punishment","(of) Hell","and for them","(is the) punishment","(of) the Burning Fire","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","fatanū","al-mu'minīna","wal-mu'mināti","thumma","lam","yatūbū","falahum","ʿadhābu","jahannama","walahum","ʿadhābu","al-ḥarīqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,2350],[3,2350,2980],[4,2980,4470],[5,4470,6070],[6,6070,7570],[7,7570,7890],[8,7890,8910],[9,8910,9710],[10,9710,10590],[11,10590,12330],[12,12330,13080],[13,13080,13970],[14,13970,17965]]}},{"name":"85:11","price":"本当に、信仰して正しい行い*を行う者たち、彼らにこそは、その下から河川が流れる楽園がある。それは大いなる勝利なのだ。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ جَنَّٰتٞ تَجۡرِي مِن تَحۡتِهَا ٱلۡأَنۡهَٰرُۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡفَوۡزُ ٱلۡكَبِيرُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5920,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna āmanū waʿamilū al-ṣāliḥāti lahum jannātun tajrī min taḥtihā al-anhāru dhālika al-fawzu al-kabīru ","translations":["Indeed","those who","believe","and do","the righteous deeds","for them","(will be) Gardens","flow","from","underneath it","the rivers","That","(is) the success","the great","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","āmanū","waʿamilū","al-ṣāliḥāti","lahum","jannātun","tajrī","min","taḥtihā","al-anhāru","dhālika","al-fawzu","al-kabīru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1600],[2,1600,2640],[3,2640,3830],[4,3830,4530],[5,4530,6020],[6,6020,6590],[7,6590,9359],[8,9359,10229],[9,10229,10859],[10,10859,12079],[11,12079,16139],[12,16139,16969],[13,16969,17799],[14,17799,21594]]}},{"name":"85:12","price":"本当にあなたの主*の（懲罰による）捕らえ方は、実に痛烈なのである。","arabic":"إِنَّ بَطۡشَ رَبِّكَ لَشَدِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5921,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna baṭsha rabbika lashadīdun ","translations":["Indeed","(the) Grip","(of) your Lord","(is) surely strong","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","baṭsha","rabbika","lashadīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,2180],[3,2180,2950],[4,2950,6495]]}},{"name":"85:13","price":"本当にかれこそは、（創造を）始められ、（それを）お戻しになるのだ。","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ يُبۡدِئُ وَيُعِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5922,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu huwa yub'di-u wayuʿīdu ","translations":["Indeed He","He","originates","and repeats","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","huwa","yub'di-u","wayuʿīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2170],[2,2170,2500],[3,2500,3470],[4,3470,7205]]}},{"name":"85:14","price":"そしてかれは、赦し深いお方、寵愛深い*お方、","arabic":"وَهُوَ ٱلۡغَفُورُ ٱلۡوَدُودُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5923,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa al-ghafūru al-wadūdu ","translations":["And He","(is) the Oft-Forgiving","the Most Loving","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","al-ghafūru","al-wadūdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,510],[2,510,1310],[3,1310,5395]]}},{"name":"85:15","price":"栄誉高き御座¹の主、","arabic":"ذُو ٱلۡعَرۡشِ ٱلۡمَجِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5924,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「御座」に関しては、高壁章５４の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"dhū al-ʿarshi al-majīdu ","translations":["Owner (of)","the Throne","the Glorious","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["dhū","al-ʿarshi","al-majīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,230],[2,230,1120],[3,1120,4665]]}},{"name":"85:16","price":"お望みのことを決行されるお方である。","arabic":"فَعَّالٞ لِّمَا يُرِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5925,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"faʿʿālun limā yurīdu ","translations":["Doer","of what","He intends","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["faʿʿālun","limā","yurīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1820],[3,1820,4835]]}},{"name":"85:17","price":"（使徒*よ、）あなたに、（自分たちの預言者*に対して集結した、不信仰な）軍勢の話は届いたか？","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡجُنُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5926,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-junūdi ","translations":["Has","come to you","(the) story","(of) the hosts","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-junūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,1220],[3,1220,2060],[4,2060,5365]]}},{"name":"85:18","price":"フィルアウン*とサムード*の（話は）？¹","arabic":"فِرۡعَوۡنَ وَثَمُودَ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5927,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ここで特にフィルアウン*とサムード*だけが取り上げられているのは、比較的後代に滅亡した前者は啓典の民*らによく知られており、一方後者は、比較的先代に滅亡したにも関わらず、アラブの地に居住していた民で、アラブ人たちによく知られていたからだと言われる（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２９８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fir'ʿawna wathamūda ","translations":["Firaun","and Thamud","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["fir'ʿawna","wathamūda",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,4695]]}},{"name":"85:19","price":"いや、不信仰に陥った者*たちは、（彼ら以前の不信仰者*たちと同様、使徒*と啓示の）噓呼ばわりをしており、","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ فِي تَكۡذِيبٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5928,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bali alladhīna kafarū fī takdhībin ","translations":["Nay","Those who","disbelieve","(are) in","denial","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["bali","alladhīna","kafarū","fī","takdhībin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,340],[2,340,1310],[3,1310,2200],[4,2200,2590],[5,2590,5945]]}},{"name":"85:20","price":"アッラー*は彼らの後方から、悉く包囲されるお方なのだ。¹","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ مِن وَرَآئِهِم مُّحِيطُۢ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5929,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アッラー*は彼らを、その知識と御力によって掌握（しょうあく）されており、彼らの行いは全てアッラー*に筒抜（つつぬ）け なのである（ムヤッサル５９０頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-lahu min warāihim muḥīṭun ","translations":["But Allah","from","behind them","encompasses","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-lahu","min","warāihim","muḥīṭun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,2070],[3,2070,5530],[4,5530,8375]]}},{"name":"85:21","price":"いや、それは栄誉高きクルアーン*¹なのである、","arabic":"بَلۡ هُوَ قُرۡءَانٞ مَّجِيدٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5930,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　つまりそれは、シルク*の徒らが主張していたような詩、占い、魔術などではなく、宗教的・現世的諸事に関する様々な教えを明らかにする、この上ない誉（ほま）れ 、高貴さ、祝福にあふれた啓典である（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：５５２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bal huwa qur'ānun majīdun ","translations":["Nay","It","(is) a Quran","Glorious","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["bal","huwa","qur'ānun","majīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,870],[3,870,1780],[4,1780,6085]]}},{"name":"85:22","price":"（いかなる改変からも無事な、）守られし碑板*の中の。","arabic":"فِي لَوۡحٖ مَّحۡفُوظِۭ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5931,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fī lawḥin maḥfūẓin ","translations":["In","a Tablet","Guarded","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","lawḥin","maḥfūẓin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,530],[2,530,1190],[3,1190,6315]]}}],"chapter":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj","Chapter Al-Buruj","Buruj","Surah Buruj","Chapter Buruj","Al Buruj","Surah Al Buruj","Chapter Al Buruj","Surah 85","Chapter 85","The Constellations","البروج"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}